{
  "texts": [
    "This is particularly useful for cases where instructors want to create a customized tool, but do not have the experience or time to create one based on the templates discussed before.",
    "We call these sorts of meta-tools \"blueprints\".",
    "Instructors can create AI tutors for students and test out those tutor prompts before giving them to students.",
    "Using an AI Tutor Blueprint the instructor can work with an AI \"instructional designer\" to create AI tutoring prompts specific to the context of their students.",
    "The AI will first ask the instructor questions about the topic they would like students to focus on, key elements of the topic or idea, and any sticking points that students generally encounter."
  ]
}